modName: Breezehome enchanting table plus lights fix
descriptionHtml:
- Adds enchanting table, storage chest and lantern in alchemy room
- Fixes glitched lights in main hall
- Adds candle in loft

Made this mainly for personal use, but thought someone else could find it useful.

Update v1.1

- Still had some flickering problems with High or lower shadows, which is fixed.
- Added version with a tilted table, since camera requires some space. Note that the alchemy table has been moved to the left in this version, if you have anything on top of it.
- Added a second tilted version (v2), with only the enchanting part rotated to give the camera more space.
author: Sina
